logicalColumns.name: Is VSOE
logicalColumns.description:
'Y' - If invoice type is 'Warranty Invoices' or 'Warranty Invoices CM'
'N' - All other Invoic's types.

Technicaly:
CASE "SSYS"."Dim - Invoice Header"."Transaction Type Name"
WHEN  'Warranty Invoices'  THEN 'Y'
WHEN  'Warranty Invoices CM'  THEN 'Y'
ELSE 'N'
END

logicalExpression.expressionTemplate: CASE %1 WHEN 'Warranty Invoices' THEN 'Y' WHEN 'Warranty Invoices CM' THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END
expressionObjects: logicalColumn:SSYS_SF.Dim - Invoice Header.Transaction Type Name (For Prompts)
